    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a practical choice for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that doesn't need to be perfect. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car drives well, there are noticeable signs of wear including some scuffs on the exterior paint and minor staining on the interior upholstery. It has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor suspension work or a tune-up in the near future. Overall, it's a solid, honest car that reflects its age and mileage fairly.",
      "price": 24500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
